{"tid":2221424,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃色經濟圈幫到好多人，但同時都錯過咗好多人","createTime":"2020-09-28T10:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T13:52:49.000Z","uid":211994,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f30af7c2c711b314ecbf9b3c3fcbaaac9675d0ab","tid":2221424,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"改一改標題開多次先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>樓主嘅資料來源：某啲手足開嘅tg channel，Terry Yeung Blog<br />\n</em><br />\n我地都知道，黃圈係以經濟打擊共產黨嘅資金來源，同為日後長期抗爭做一個準備（如有錯煩請指正）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>然而，唔計中共大外宣，有一班勇武前線係真心覺得黃圈助用唔大、廢</strong><br />\n<br />\n有一班手足一個禮拜生活費只有幾十蚊<br />\n佢地一個禮拜都係食公仔麵同出前一丁，一日有兩餐已經叫好<br />\n佢地冇護照/見光死而冇得搵工<br />\n喺屋企捱杯麵之餘，又要健身同買野個陣<br />\n佢地見到一班相對犧牲冇咁大嘅人<br />\n用四五六十蚊食一餐黃店<br />\n唔駛驚會有一日俾人滅口<br />\n仲叫班前線「去打工啦<br />\n咁大個人有手有腳唔係唔做野下話」<br />\n心入面當然唔好過<br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"gold\">我聽過有啲手足係咁講：<br />\n「你幾時見過有一個國家嘅軍人要出去賺錢養自己買裝去打仗？」</span></em><br />\n<br />\n黃圈嘅錢好少會流入前線抗爭者手上<br />\n正確啲講，只有出名嘅人先會到幫助<br />\n<br />\n呢個係邏輯上無解，出名嘅人自然就會安全啲，其他人提供支援嘅風險都低啲<br />\n你可以同人講你patreon有份subscribe黃之鋒沈旭暉<br />\n但你唔會想有人知你今日助養咗邊一位無名嘅抗爭者，一有人知，到時就齊齊監倉見<br />\n隨時間推移，有名氣嘅人得到嘅資源越滾越大<br />\n冇名氣嘅，幫助佢嘅渠道冇得公開，幫到佢嘅人只會越嚟越少<br />\n<br />\n我唔係指責有名氣嘅抗爭者/提供支援咁多位家長，只係描述現況<br />\n<br />\n咁要點做呢，自己諗，自己搵<br />\n<br />\n其實我都係拾人牙慧，想知多少少可以睇下呢篇文<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CFjhrFKnlHa/?igshid=10vu4qalyt3vn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFjhrFKnlHa%2F%3Figshid%3D10vu4qalyt3vn&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=e997cd6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCFjhrFKnlHa%2F%3Figshid%3D10vu4qalyt3vn&h=58407be3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CFjhrFKnlHa/?igshid=10vu4qalyt3vn</a>"},{"pid":"4afdc1d757a04236d602fe5b750714221f590b83","tid":2221424,"uid":54927,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"班人唔係真係當左自己軍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2147d726c540fa62eb014027be580140af0a0d03","tid":2221424,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fed8d6193645f78a3a7d3b298ddd311aca9e22d","tid":2221424,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:30:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f3513056d4d0a83fe5657c63f321dc34b1b732f","tid":2221424,"uid":173814,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:33:27.000Z","msg":"養肥一班老闆加人工俾自己買車供樓姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334dd982c865bb2b9279529138741a13d1f78bbb","tid":2221424,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:46:32.000Z","msg":"我話眾籌俾錢你打仗，你敢要咩？"},{"pid":"7c64acafcfabc8cd8798a8a660582cc0150593f3","tid":2221424,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"又夠鐘分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20a138428267feee89152c7085cb0e8f09554cd","tid":2221424,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49ca0fc39d8f287b40d7b0f05bf4cb9f0824c072","tid":2221424,"uid":223643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"其實做生意一樣好重要嘅嘢，<br />\n就係要有發展<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃圈要有發展，要壯大，<br />\n如果唔係就變咗買紀念品"},{"pid":"5ad2cb02fa0c0eb9bcee5785c124ce61f4ce71af","tid":2221424,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:01:12.000Z","msg":"又話兄弟爬山各有各做，又想鬥黃到幾時啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e84daa80a0c45d75fa69d08d91b1a961063ec1","tid":2221424,"uid":5725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:07:59.000Z","msg":"事實係， 大家無組織既自發活動， 最多只係做得到咁<br />\n我諗佢都提唔到有咩可行建議"},{"pid":"0db0c42765d21a20e1dd99b2315413cfb5f2d85e","tid":2221424,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"笑"},{"pid":"1390a80c2bae84598d287daf8c5ea26bb8fb8f00","tid":2221424,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4388c8c7741c0d2ec7d3c1effc7a43c39c5d8b17","tid":2221424,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25e84daa80a0c45d75fa69d08d91b1a961063ec1","tid":2221424,"uid":5725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:07:59.000Z","msg":"事實係， 大家無組織既自發活動， 最多只係做得到咁<br />\n我諗佢都提唔到有咩可行建議"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:36:18.000Z","msg":"事實係去到呢個階段無有型既組織係無咩可能突破到個困境<br />\n但香港所有SO CALLED民主派甚至乎本土派組織都做唔到多方信任"},{"pid":"467242b38b3d8b60a0ca8237e000b27393da6706","tid":2221424,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:39:30.000Z","msg":"佢地冇護照/見光死而冇得搵工 II都係手足？"},{"pid":"1cd88469522c9aec2bcd2f93cc24bec9ab1c9331","tid":2221424,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:40:46.000Z","msg":"某啲手足開嘅tg channel<br />\n<br />\n熱狗個前列腺有話兒？"},{"pid":"77ff8417cc854ab12eb483a79f05a8aae105fa9d","tid":2221424,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:51:27.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈生意手法嚟啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5050a2b9a5de3f8cd300ddd4de532bf7522ea304","tid":2221424,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4388c8c7741c0d2ec7d3c1effc7a43c39c5d8b17","tid":2221424,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25e84daa80a0c45d75fa69d08d91b1a961063ec1","tid":2221424,"uid":5725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:07:59.000Z","msg":"事實係， 大家無組織既自發活動， 最多只係做得到咁<br />\n我諗佢都提唔到有咩可行建議"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:36:18.000Z","msg":"事實係去到呢個階段無有型既組織係無咩可能突破到個困境<br />\n但香港所有SO CALLED民主派甚至乎本土派組織都做唔到多方信任"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"坦白講<br />\n去大台化碎片化就有咁既情況發生<br />\n因為每個人都係個體式行動 甚至選擇唔相信任何團體組織<br />\n<br />\n但另外 有個自己養得起自己既經濟圈亦好重要<br />\n經濟獨立 你上網都唔怕用番真名<br />\n唔使好似公務員或者老師咁 要扮愛黨愛國"}]}